<h3>Payment</h3>
<p>During the profile creation process, you will have the chance to choose your hourly rate. For students, you find in the Amozek marketplace, Amozek will keep a commission of 10%-30% on each lesson you have. As you work more hours through the marketplace, the more money you'll take home. Since you're independent, your portion will be distributed with no taxes or fees withheld.</p>

<p>Students pay you through the Amozek payment system for all tutoring services. You can choose to receive bimonthly payment via check or direct deposit.</p>